reviewText: Such a fun movie. My kids ask me to put the movie over and over again And what is even better, is not one of those that you get tired to see over time.

Had to send it back because it wouldn't work on my DVD.  Cost a lot of $$$ to do so since it had to go back to Germany!  There should be more warnings about foreign codes on some movies...would make shopping easier.

This movie is so under rated compared to other recent Disney releases it is sad. Better than Frozen as far as I am concerned. The animation and the story line is nothing short of genious. Moral story is heartwarming but not preachy.
Great movie that my daughter can't get enough of.  Can't wait for the sequel!

Bought this for my 2 1/2 year old grandson and when we went to watch it with him it did not work.  It said something about region code.  Regardless it was very difficult to make him understand that he could not watch his favorite movie.
Worked fine. Happy with the lower price.
